list.name: Changes
list.comment: feat: redesign InsightAudio pipeline (jobs, sessions, tabs, quality controls) * add background job processing (Celery + Redis) with persistent Job/User storage * implement “My Jobs” list + secure downloads for recent results * split UI into Audio / Documents / My Jobs tabs * expose key ASR quality params (language, presets, beam/temp/VAD) + fix whisper-large-v3 parsing * add prompt templates + per-run custom summary prompt and LLM quality knobs * replace fake progress with server-driven stages + ETA * unify results storage, fix speaker labels without diarization, and make caches param-aware
